effect. It was a request of the athletic 
department. Yes, yeah, yeah, yeah. That you did

22:13.100 --> 22:19.667
the

22:13.100 --> 22:19.667
voice of Kyle Fitts. Yeah, the voice of Kyle Fitts. 
