22:35.493 --> 22:38.898
refereed football for quite a few years. I 
belonged to the SFOA. And that's how I got into this

22:41.863 --> 22:46.029
athletic business. I've been fiddling around in 
athletics either as a player or a coach. spectator

22:54.263 --> 22:57.587
or announcer for about 50 years. I've done 
